Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.52,0:00:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣，繼續上週的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.22,0:00:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克他們仍在迷宮裡迷路中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.39,0:00:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離上次已經一星期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克真是個路癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子說我…嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此我就留在佛雷姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.73,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和隔壁的女孩子約會都比這好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.61,0:00:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是擤鼻涕的時候嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.23,0:00:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.31,0:00:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰!快點出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.21,0:00:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有氣魄!但是只有台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.49,0:00:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑的話就沒志氣喔，史派克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.09,0:00:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…該不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.79,0:00:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由騎士潘恩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊，已經迷路近一個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓，有沒有食物啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.11,0:01:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…所謂的騎士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.68,0:01:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時，都要保持冷靜\N與騎士的自尊才行喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有說服力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.05,0:01:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘恩是因為擔心我的情況\N所以才來看我對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看!在拍攝呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.19,0:01:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸運了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現自己還太嫩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.46,0:01:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論遭遇任何作戰\N都不可大意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.87,0:01:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會順利的完成這個任務\N然後成為一名優秀的騎士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今後我一定要保護好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.78,0:01:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?潘恩?蒂德?\N你們在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好那兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.85,0:01:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太久沒有登場\N所以只想搶鏡頭吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個也該適可而止吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就減少我們的出場了嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
